rpc.trackingDetails: The Living Assets network does not store any personal data provided by its users. The network solely communicates on-chain signatures generated by web3 compatible wallets. However, it is possible that clients utilizing the network may necessitate supplementary information from their users to fulfill Know Your Customer obligations. In such cases, explicit consent from the users is mandatory, following standard procedures.
